recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large frying pan. Add beef and cook for 5 minutes, stirring with a wooden spoon to break up any lumps. Add red capsicum, Taco Spice Mix and stir for 1 minute. Add 1/2 cup water and simmer for 2 minutes or until sauce thickens.
